    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have to see this absolute beauty in person! It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and smells like it just left the showroom. I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of it, so there isn't a single blemish to find. It drives incredibly smooth and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a total gem that's been loved every mile, this is the one for you! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
