    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to be listing this absolute gem. It\u2019s in pristine, showroom-quality condition\u2014seriously, you\u2019ve got to see it to believe it! It's been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and still has that fresh, new-car feel inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot, this is the one for you. Swing by and take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
