      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a comprehensive service history including preventative rod bearing replacement and a full VANOS system overhaul. The chassis integrity is verified with a reinforced rear subframe, and the power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to an M-Variable limited-slip differential. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation, the vehicle retains factory suspension geometry and staggered Style 67 alloy wheels. This is a purist-spec example with no deferred maintenance, providing a direct, tactile driving experience that remains the benchmark for the M-division.",
